import PyPDF2

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/7-bertscore/bert_score/paper.pdf'
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    num_pages = len(reader.pages)
    text = ''
    for i in range(num_pages):
        text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'

# Show the first 2000 characters to inspect
text[:2000]
